'''马里恩军事学院'''{{noteTag|1=地名“Marion”在中国大陆译作“-{zh-hans:马里恩;zh-hant:馬里恩}-”<ref>{{Cite web|title=世界地名翻译大辞典|url=http://mall.cnki.net/reference/ref_search.aspx?bid=R200807101&inputText=Marion|accessdate=2020-02-07|work=mall.cnki.net}}</ref>。}}（{{lang-en|'''Marion Military Institute'''}}，简称：{{lang|en|'''MMI'''{{noteTag|1=有时也简称为'''Marion Institute'''，'''Marion Military'''，或'''Marion'''。}}}}）于1842年在[[美國|美國]][[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[马里恩_(阿拉巴马州)|马里恩市]]創校，在该国仅有的4所[[美国军事初级院校|军事初级学院]]中历史最为悠久<ref name="AlabamaEncyclopedia">{{en}}{{Cite web |url=http://www.encyclopediaofalabama.org/article/h-3704 |title=Marion Military Institute |accessdate=2017-06-09 |date= |publisher=Encyclopedia of Alabama |last=Encyclopedia of Alabama |year=2008 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2017-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609234355/http://www.encyclopediaofalabama.org/article/h-3704 |ref=harv }}</ref>。因其为阿拉巴马州法定的官方[[军校|军事学府]]，所以又名'''阿拉巴马军事学院'''（'''the Military College of Alabama'''<ref>{{en}}{{Cite book|last=Mohr|first=Clarence L.|title=《The New Encyclopedia of Southern Culture: Volume 17: Education》|publisher=UNC Press Books|year=2011|page=81|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XP1mBK2ezzQC&dq=the+military+college+of+alabama&source=gbs_navlinks_s|deadurl=no|isbn=0807877859|ref=harv|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327030150/https://books.google.com/books?id=XP1mBK2ezzQC&dq=the+military+college+of+alabama&source=gbs_navlinks_s|archivedate=2018-03-27}}</ref>）。马里恩军事学院是{{Link-en|南方院校协会|Southern Association of Colleges and Schools}}的成员之一，有“'''美国[[伊顿公学|伊顿]]'''”之称<ref name="NM">{{en}}{{Cite book|last1=Brayley|first1=Arthur Wellington|last2=Tarbell|first2=Arthur Winslow|last3=Chapple|first3=Joe Mitchell|title=《National Magazine, Volume 34》|publisher=Bostonian publishing Company|year=1911|page=460|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5kUPAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA460&dq=%22American+eton%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjsr5WN3qjWAhVr5oMKHRphCS0Q6AEIQDAE#v=onepage&q=%22American%20eton%22&f=false|deadurl=no|ref=harv|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916031250/https://books.google.com/books?id=5kUPAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA460&dq=%22American+eton%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjsr5WN3qjWAhVr5oMKHRphCS0Q6AEIQDAE#v=onepage&q=%22American%20eton%22&f=false|archivedate=2017-09-16}}</ref>，曾被评为卓越荣誉军事学校、最佳军事初级学院、全美最成功的[[社区学院|社区学院]]第12位、最佳社区学院第16位、阿拉巴马州校友收入最高的社区学院等<ref name="GoArmy">{{en}}{{Cite web |url=https://www.goarmy.com/rotc/schools/marion-military-institute/history.html |title=Marion Military Institute |accessdate=2017-06-09 |date= |publisher=GoArmy.com |last=GoArmy.com |year=2017 |ref=harv |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609230937/https://www.goarmy.com/rotc/schools/marion-military-institute/history.html |archivedate=2017-06-09 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/pf/college/community-colleges/ |title=How Does Your Community College Stack Up? |accessdate=2017-06-09 |date= |publisher=CNN Money |last=CNN Money |year=2012 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2017-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609232431/http://money.cnn.com/pf/college/community-colleges/ |ref=harv }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/pf/college/community-colleges/ |title=MMI Ranked #16 in Nation among Community Colleges |accessdate=2017-06-09 |date= |publisher=WSFA-12 (NBC) |last=WSFA |year=2017 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2017-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609233024/http://www.wsfa.com/story/22599868/mmi-ranked-16-in-nation-among-community-colleges |ref=harv }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |url=https://collegescorecard.ed.gov/search/?degree=a&state=AL&control=public&sort=salary:desc |title=College Scorecard |accessdate=2017-08-05 |date= |publisher=U.S. Department of Education |last=U.S. Department of Education |year=2017 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2017-08-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805181744/https://collegescorecard.ed.gov/search/?degree=a&state=AL&control=public&sort=salary:desc |ref=harv }}</ref>。马里恩的军校学员团绰号'''猛虎营'''（'''Bold Tiger Battalion'''<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web |url=https://marionmilitary.edu/incoming-ecp-cadets-prepare-for-fort-knox/ |title=Incoming ECP cadets prepare for Fort Knox |accessdate=2017-09-15 |date= |publisher=Marion Military Institute |last=Marion Military Institute |year=2017 |deadurl=no |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906091158/https://marionmilitary.edu/incoming-ecp-cadets-prepare-for-fort-knox/ |archivedate=2017-09-06 }}</ref>），除了自身的陆军军官课程外，也是美国五大[[美国联邦军事院校|联邦军校]]官方指定的[[预科|预科]]之一<ref name="SAP">{{en}}{{Cite web |url=https://marionmilitary.edu/service-academy-program-sap/ |title=Service Academy Program (SAP) |accessdate=2017-09-05 |date= |publisher=Marion Military Institute |last=Marion Military Institute |year= |deadurl=yes |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906091931/https://marionmilitary.edu/service-academy-program-sap/ |archivedate=2017-09-06 }}</ref>。自建校一百余年以来，包括一位[[美利坚联盟国|美利坚联盟国]]准将在内的[[美军|美军]]各个军种共有超过200名将军毕业于该校<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0405/17/lol.01.html |title=Transcripts |accessdate=2017-06-09 |date= |publisher=CNN |last=CNN |year=2004 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2017-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609233405/http://www.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0405/17/lol.01.html |ref=harv }}</ref><ref name="MMIGENADM">
